OL,7,FTwo police officers will appear in
OL,8,Fcourt charged with assaulting an
OL,9,Felderly disabled man in a dementia
OL,10,Fcare home in East Sussex.
OL,12,FPc Stephen Smith, 50, and Pc Rachel
OL,13,FComotto, 34, are charged with assault
OL,14,Foccasioning actual bodily harm after
OL,15,Ftheir use of force against 93-year-old
OL,16,FDonald Burgess.
