OL,4,Cover assault on disabled man in care
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FThe Sussex Police officers had
OL,8,Fattended the unit in St Leonards-on-
OL,9,FSea after a report of a resident with
OL,10,Fa knife threatening staff on June 21
OL,11,F2022.
OL,13,FA Taser, an incapacitant spray,
OL,14,Fhandcuffs and a baton were used on Mr
OL,15,FBurgess who was taken to hospital
OL,16,Fafter the incident.
OL,18,FThe 93-year-old died in hospital three
OL,19,Fweeks later.
