OL,7,FWatchdog the Independent Office for
OL,8,FPolice Conduct (IOPC) said evidence
OL,9,Fdid not show the incident caused or
OL,10,Fcontributed to his death.
OL,12,FThe criminal proceedings come after
OL,13,Fthe IOPC investigation which began
OL,14,Fwith a voluntary referral from Sussex
OL,15,FPolice in June 2022.
OL,17,FThe investigation was completed six
OL,18,Fmonths later with a file of evidence
OL,19,Fbeing given to the Crown Prosecution
OL,20,FService in June 2023.
