OL,7,FSmith is charged with two counts of
OL,8,Factual bodily harm, and Comotto is
OL,9,Fcharged with one count of actual
OL,10,Fbodily harm.
OL,12,FThe pair will appear at Westminster
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on April 25.
OL,15,FIOPC director Mel Palmer said: "Our
OL,16,Fthoughts remain with Mr Burgess's
OL,17,Ffamily and everyone affected by this
OL,18,Fincident.
